channel.title: FALLEN-wars 317 RSPS check it out! [link finally fixed]
channel.description:
[b]first of all i wanna say that this was a renegadepkz rsps was but i cleaned up and reworked a little and i started my codering carrier with this rsps but now that i'm coding higher rsps's now i started with much higher rsps codering and i never used this one anymore so i tought it might be time to buplish this for everyone that want to start coding hope you enjoy this.[/b]
[b][center]i am working on my v2 of this cool project with some luck it will be up on moparscape soon ;) thanks for those nice comments btw i really respect that :') [/center][/b]
[b]things that are in the game[/b]
all working skills bosses pvp area's skilling shops slayer master cosmetic shops pk shops donator shops chaotics skilling area minigames (pest control, barrows, fight pits, etc etc...) training teleports (rock crabs, dagganoths, slayer tower, etc etc...) staffzone donatorzone highscores working gnome agility course
[b]things i wanted to add but never had the time for it[/b]
barbarian agility the skill farming the skill construction the skill summoning new armour (like torva, pernix, virtus,....) pets more bosses
some pictures of the rsps how it looks like to give you guys a idea
inlog screen [img]http://i48.tinypic.com/2quuptw.png[/img] home [img]http://i47.tinypic.com/160vhjo.png[/img] skilling area [img]http://i48.tinypic.com/14oc9zo.png[/img] [img]http://i47.tinypic.com/1z1srrq.png[/img] bosses [img]http://i45.tinypic.com/50scpg.png[/img] [img]http://i47.tinypic.com/vzvsxs.png[/img] [img]http://i50.tinypic.com/20szuhf.png[/img] daganoths for training (1 of the 5 cb training area's) [img]http://i46.tinypic.com/16iab2r.png[/img] minigames [img]http://i49.tinypic.com/122k8ee.png[/img] dungeoneering shop [img]http://i47.tinypic.com/2cghr1s.png[/img] working slayer task [img]http://i46.tinypic.com/303ivza.png[/img]
hope that are enough pics :D
[b]remember i just used this for practice[/b]
[b]credits go to renegadepkz because its the client that belongs to him and that i used to practice[/b]
client and source: http://www.mijnbestand.nl/Bestand-VABC3UNLAUGD.rar sorry that it took so long :/
